### Welcome
GET http://localhost:3000/



### Create Event 1
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "UOG Software Engineering Society Hackathon",
  "totalSeats": 3,
  "eventDate": "2026-09-10"
}


### Create Event 2
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "UOG Debating Society Championship",
  "totalSeats": 5,
  "eventDate": "2026-11-20"
}


### Create Event 3
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "UOG Annual Sports Gala",
  "totalSeats": 10,
  "eventDate": "2027-02-20"
}


### Get All Events
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events


### Get Events Sorted by Date
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events?sort=date


### Get Upcoming Events Only
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events?upcoming=true


### Get Single Event
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/1


### Error - Event Not Found
GET http://localhost:3000/api/events/999


### Error - Past Date
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Old Event",
  "totalSeats": 10,
  "eventDate": "2020-01-01"
}


### Error - Duplicate Event Name
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "UOG Software Engineering Society Hackathon",
  "totalSeats": 10,
  "eventDate": "2027-01-01"
}


### Error - Zero Seats
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bad Event",
  "totalSeats": 0,
  "eventDate": "2027-01-01"
}


### Error - Negative Seats
POST http://localhost:3000/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bad Event",
  "totalSeats": -5,
  "eventDate": "2027-01-01"
}


### Update Event
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/events/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "UOG SE Society Hackathon 2026",
  "totalSeats": 10
}


### Delete Event (Event 3 - No Registrations)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/events/3


### Register User 1
POST http://localhost:3000/api/registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "Ahmad",
  "eventId": 1
}


