### View Active Registrations for Event 1
GET http://localhost:3000/api/registrations/event/1


### Cancel Registration
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/registrations/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "Ahmad",
  "eventId": 1
}


### Cancel Already Cancelled - Should Fail
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/registrations/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "Ahmad",
  "eventId": 1
}


### Re-register After Cancel - Should Succeed
POST http://localhost:3000/api/registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userName": "Ahmad",
  "eventId": 1
}


### View Active Registrations After Re-register
GET http://localhost:3000/api/registrations/event/1